        <div class="bodysection">
            <div class="body" itemprop="about" data-fieldname="body" data-bind="htmlValue:body">
<p>Night &amp; Fog in Japan openly displays the director’s disappointment with the left wing movement in the light of the US-Japan security Treaty talks.</p>
<p>Using avant-garde techniques of clashing archival material with stylized drama, this is Oshima’s most explicitly political film in both form and content.</p></div>
        </div>

